parameters: Is this like a break room? There's even a bed.

The path ahead might be the magic circle from
earlier. Should we go back?
Yeah. But can we take a short break?
Masamune-kun just received healing magic as well.

(Being alone with Amelia in a locked room...
There's no way I wouldn't be nervous)

(We've just started dating. It's only natural to
be conscious of that)

(Or rather, I suddenly got excited after entering
the room)
Why is your down there getting bigger...?

I understand how you feel... but we're on a
mission right now.

I-It's not like I intended for that to happen. My
body just reacted on its own...

Just so you know, it's not about my body. I really
love you.

I understand. But we have to do something about
it.

(This is not the time to have an erection. Calm
down, me.)
I'm the one making it big...
If you keep looking at that, I'll get horny too.

No, I'm surprised to hear Amelia say something
like that. I thought you were bad with dirty
jokes.

Well, it's not like I don't have any sexual
desire.
Well, I do it like a normal person.
No, not at all. I mean, I'm happy.
Why are you happy when I do it alone...

Speaking of which, if we keep talking like this,
it'll never end.

(Both of our gazes unintentionally go towards the
bed)

It can't be helped. Even though we're lovers, I'm
still your older sister, so I'll lend you a hand.

Ugh... I'm still embarrassed. Even during sex, I
ended up saying some really naughty things, didn't
I?

I was just caught up in the excitement. I mean,
even I was swept away during my first time.

So, it seems like my down there has gotten
smaller, right?

For now, I'm glad. With this, it seems like we can
move forward.
From now on, it's work mode.
We can do it anytime after we're done.
(I still feel embarrassed by the word 'lovers').
